  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Experience</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container flex flex-col mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Data Science Intern at GovTech"
      subtitle="Jan 2026 to May 2026 at GovTech, Singapore"
      logo="/logos/govtech.png"
    >
      Built multimodal AI systems using RF-DETR, Gemini 3, Qwen-TTS/STT, and SAM3 for Whole-of-Government applications. Developed RAG pipelines and agentic vision workflows. Managed cloud infrastructure with Docker, AWS, GCP, GPU-backed inference, and DGX Spark. Contributed to GovTech Multimodal Hub.
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Data Scientist Intern at Tictag"
      subtitle="Jun 2025 to Aug 2025 at Tictag, Singapore"
      logo="/logos/tictag.png"
    >
      Designed and implemented scalable deep learning models for computer vision, speech, and video analytics. Built modular ETL pipelines for fine-tuning and production-ready workflows for pose classification and ROI event tracking. Delivered business insights from CCTV footage using segmentation and depth models.
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Undergraduate Teaching Assistant for CS2040"
      subtitle="Aug 2024 to Dec 2025 at NUS School of Computing, Singapore"
      logo="/logos/nus.png"
    >
      Conducted weekly tutorials on data structures and algorithms in Java for 30 students (AY24/25 and AY25/26). Guided lab sessions and graded assignments. Honour Roll recipient.
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Climate Models Analytics Intern"
      subtitle="May 2024 to Aug 2024 at DSTA, Singapore"
      logo="/logos/dsta.png"
      isLast={true}
    >
      Built a robust pipeline with Selenium and APIs to automate weather data retrieval. Enhanced rainfall analysis using super-resolution models (SRGAN, RDN). Deployed a Llama-based offline chatbot to support domain experts in meteorology.
